Buyer Experience:
- Enter the website
- View homepage with slides, popular products, video teaser, and categories
- Navigate to products page
- Filter products by categories and price
- View product details
- Add products to cart
- View cart with total price
- Proceed to checkout
- Recieve order confirmation via Email


Admin Experience
- Get Notified of new orders via email
- View 'Orders' Page for. Update status ke 'Terkonfirmasi'
- Update order status as 'Terkirim'


Out of Scopes:
- Payment Method other than QRIS
- Chat, Comment & Review
- Wishlist
- Multi Languages
    - English

